sentence: In trading on Tuesday, shares of Home Depot Inc (Symbol: HD) crossed below their 200 day moving average of $78.14, changing hands as low as $77.84 per share.
Home Depot Inc shares are currently trading off about 0.9% on the day.

The chart below shows the one year performance of HD shares, versus its 200 day moving average:

Looking at the chart above, HD's low point in its 52 week range is $72.21 per share, with $83.20 as the 52 week high point - that compares with a last trade of $77.99.
According to the ETF Finder at ETF Channel, HD makes up 12.71% of the PowerShares Dynamic Building & Construction Portfolio ETF (Symbol: PKB) which is trading lower by about 0.2% on the day Tuesday.
